article.description: — Amadou Sow had 18 points as UC Santa Barbara topped Idaho State 56-43 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Sow carries UC Santa Barbara over Idaho State 56-43
article.linkText: Sow carries UC Santa Barbara over Idaho State 56-43
article.story: SANTA BARBARA, Calif. -- — Amadou Sow had 18 points as UC Santa Barbara topped Idaho State 56-43 on Wednesday. Ajay Mitchell had 14 points for UC Santa Barbara (7-4), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Tarik Cool had 11 points and six rebounds for the Bengals (2-9). Austin Smellie added seven assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
